<li id="cite_note-135"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-135">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web">Aquinas, Thomas. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://ethics.sandiego.edu/Books/Texts/Aquinas/JustWar.html">"Part II, Question 40"</a>. <i>The Summa Theologica</i>. Benziger Bros. edition, 1947<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://ethics.sandiego.edu/Books/Texts/Aquinas/JustWar.html">http://ethics.sandiego.edu/Books/Texts/Aquinas/JustWar.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 8/1/2011</span>.</span></span></li>
