<li>Angelo Codevilla and Paul Seabury, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.toreadnext.com/9781574886108"><i>War: Ends and Means</i></a> (Potomac Books, Revised second edition by Angelo Codevilla, 2006) ISBN-X</li>
